david wickham executive profile  biography  bloomberg july    pm et capital markets company overview of hsbc global asset management uk limited snapshotpeople  overviewboard memberscommittees executive profile david wickham director and senior product specialist  hsbc global asset management uk limitedagetotal calculated compensationthis person is connected to  board members in  different organizations across  different industries background mr david wickham is the director and senior product specialist at hsbc global asset management uk limited he is responsible for global emerging market equities prior to joining hsbc mr wickham was the director of private equity investments at invesco private capital ipc he joined the firm in  and left in january  mr wickham was based in the london office and focused on the quantitative and qualitative analysis of prospective partnership fund investments  prior to joining ipc mr wickham was a director and member of the private equity investment committee at insight investment in london and was primarily responsible for sourcing analyzing approving and monitoring private equity partnership investments in europe and north america before moving to the uk mr wickham had worked in australia at mercer global investments and also at jana investment advisers in melbourne as a consultant on private equity performing research on funds and formalizing portfolio allocation strategies mr wickham earned a bachelor of business in economics and finance from the royal melbourne institute of technology a graduate certificate in management from the australian graduate school of management at the university of new south wales and is currently completing a master’s program in international relations at cambridge universityread full background corporate headquarters first floorlondon greater london swa ejunited kingdomphone fax  board members memberships there is no board members memberships data available education there is no education data availabl