rs the account fee will be payable by you for the services we provide when arranging the sale and purchase of fund shares in clean share classes as well as custody and administration of those fund shares when they are held in your account full details of charges including annual management charges and any other expenses are available in the key features document and the individual fund details is there a minimum amount that i have to invest the minimum initial investment is £ for each class of fund shares for each portfolio the minimum additional investment is also £ what happens after i have placed a buy instruction if a buy instruction is placed prior to the dealing deadline for individual dealing deadlines please see the fund details document for the specific fund then your order will normally be placed with the fund provider before the funds next valuation point the valuation point for each fund is shown in the fund details you can then view the status of an instruction by clicking on details located within the my order status section once we receive confirmation that the instruction has been executed by the fund provider your new holding will be reflected within my fund portfolio section when you place a buy instruction a hold will be placed on the required monies in your chosen settlement account or in the case of your isa this will be the uninvested cash account the money will be taken from your settlement account or your uninvested cash account on settlement day we will send you a confirmation of the number of fund shares purchased for you and the price you paid can i make regular contributions to a fund or make a joint application no we dont currently offer this service for global investment centre however you may invest as often as you like subject to the minimum investment amount of £ for each fund for each account investment risk all investments carry some risk the value of investments and any income received from them can fall as well as rise and you ma